# Cursor AI Assistant Rules for @finografic Packages

## Package Development

- This is a standalone npm package, not a monorepo
- Use TypeScript throughout with strict mode
- Follow existing patterns and conventions
- Focus on creating reusable, well-typed utilities

## Development Workflow

- DO NOT start development servers unless explicitly requested
- The user manages their own development instances
- Focus on code quality, type safety, and maintainability
- Ensure all exports are properly typed and documented

## Project Structure

- Source code in `src/`
- Built output in `dist/`
- Examples in `src/utils/examples/`
- Use TypeScript throughout
- Follow existing patterns and conventions
